==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Thornbird
<hw>Thorn"bird`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A small South American bird (<spn>Anumbius anumbii</spn>) allied to
the ovenbirds of the genus <gen>Furnarius</gen>). It builds a very large
and complex nest of twigs and thorns in a bush or tree.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

